casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Nicholas James PATTON, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158285
COA: 341105 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 14, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the stipulation signed by counsel for the parties agreeing to the dismissal of this application for leave to appeal is considered, and the application for leave to appeal is DISMISSED with prejudice.
